    <item>
      <title>阿达尼·格林制定了偿还 7.5 亿美元债券的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/adani-green-lays-out-initial-plan-for-repaying-750-million-bond</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿达尼集团旗下太阳能部门公布了偿还明年到期的 7.5 亿美元债券的初步蓝图，随着这家印度企业集团在今年早些时候市场暴跌后重建信心，债务上涨势头得以延续。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/adani-green-lays-out-initial-plan-for-repaying-750-million-bond</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Dec 2023 02:23:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着焦点从日本央行投机转向美国数据，日元波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/yen-extends-rally-to-second-day-as-traders-bet-on-early-boj-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日元波动，放弃了周五的大部分涨幅，因为焦点从对日本央行近期政策转变的猜测转向当天晚些时候公布的美国就业数据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/yen-extends-rally-to-second-day-as-traders-bet-on-early-boj-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Dec 2023 01:50:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市稳定，紧张等待美国就业数据：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/japanese-shares-eye-early-slump-after-yen-surge-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股市和美国期货保持窄幅波动，交易员等待关键的美国就业报告，以获取更多证据来证明劳动力市场是否冷却得足够快，从而使美联储更接近降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/japanese-shares-eye-early-slump-after-yen-surge-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 22:56:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
